connect the RXD, TXD and GNG to the three pins next to eth.
The pin towards the mini-USB-port is RXD, the one in the middle is TXD and the last one GND.

the pin next to the screw is GND.
the pin in the middle is TXD
the pin towards USB_OTG is RXD

on openSUSE add your user to the "dialout"-group or create a udev-rule to change permission and run:
Â£ screen /dev/ttyUSB0 115200
(or just be root)
